reviewText: This is a wonderful movie the whole family can enjoy together.  It's a delightful comedy full of mistaken identities and clever cover stories.  Filled with compelling characters as well as quite a few laughs, this is a sure bet for family movie night.  Although the acting is sometimes quite horrible, in my opinion it only adds to the appeal.  This is a B movie that earns an A+!
